title: Harry_Potter_and_the_Deathly_Hallows_Part 1_DVD_Rip_ISO
description:
Voldemort's power is growing stronger. He now has control over the Ministry of Magic and Hogwarts. Harry, Ron, and Hermione decide to finish Dumbledore's work and find the rest of the Horcruxes to defeat the Dark Lord. But little hope remains for the Trio, and the rest of the Wizarding World, so everything they do must go as planned. Written by Chris Green. (http://www.imdb.com)



DVD released: 11th April 2011
